*DESCRIPTION_START
This large area is outfitted with all kinds of smithing gear. A forge stands
along the eastern wall, against the inside of the Citadel wall, being fed by
a pair of laborers. All kinds of smithing is done here, from the making of
chains for the gates to the crafting of fine weapons for use by the soldiers. 
An arch leads to the parade ground and the forge area extends further south.
*DESCRIPTION_END
