*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand atop the Citadel overlooking the gate. Peering over the wall affords
you a view of the street below. The ramparts continue to the east and west,
while a spiral staircase leads back down to the parade grounds. Iron lanterns
are placed into the wall at even intervals along the ramparts and at every
tower. Above the gate is a flagpole bearing two flags that fly in the breeze.
*DESCRIPTION_END
