*DESCRIPTION_START
This tower provides a sweeping view of the northwestern portion of Fayd,
including the tower of the Silver Arcana and the Royal Palace. Far to the
north, the peaks of the Teeth of Shartan are visible. To the west can be
seen the mighty Eltinmar river and the foreboding Grymwood forest. You can
see the street below over the edge of the wall, and you can see the south
tower from here, all is clear. The ramparts continue to the east.
*DESCRIPTION_END
