CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This tower provides a majestic view of the northeastern portion of Fayd and
the surrounding countryside. Commerce can be seen traversing the streets of
Fayd and the road leading to the farms to the east. You can see the street
below over the edge of the wall, and you can see the south tower from here,
all is clear. The ramparts continue to the west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
