NUMBER 2712
NAME Hallway of Warriors, North
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Situated upon either wall are more portraits of past and present members
of the Crimson Band. An archway to the west leads to the arena, while the
hallway extends further south. The north end of the hall ends in a door
with a large flag above it, leading into the enlisted barracks.
*DESCRIPTION_END
