ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This short, spartan hallway off of the War Room leads to the officer's
quarters. The opening to the officer's area is guarded by two soldiers
at all times. On the southern wall of the corridor are a pair of doors.
