NUMBER 2715
NAME Citadel, High Lord's Office
ASTRAL 
DARKNESS
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is the office of the current High Lord of the Crimson Band. The floor is 
covered by a finely woven crimson and silver rug of Aelfen weave. Near the 
center of the room is a large mirmach desk. Behind the desk is a comfortable
looking overstuffed crimson leather armchair. In the southwest corner of the
room stands a fearsome stuffed Kvantar warrior. In front of the desk are two 
smaller oak chairs. Shelves line the western wall, displaying an assortment
of books and war mementos. A portrait of the Crimson Band's first High Lord 
adorns the eastern wall. Beneath the painting is a sofa with an ursine fur 
cover. The room is lit by ruby studded silver lanterns situated to either 
side of a window located in the southern wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
