NUMBER 2716
NAME Citadel, Specialized Training
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This barren chamber is used by the Crimson Band to teach some of
the more esoteric or less accepted skills to its members. Many of
the teachers here are injured veterans who chose to spend their
time teaching their unique skills rather than seek retirement.
*DESCRIPTION_END
