NUMBER 2719
NAME Citadel, Arena Entrance
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This bare room is the vestibule to the Crimson Band arena. The stone walls
are bare of any trappings and are cool to the touch. To the northwest is a
stairway, above which is a sign labeled "Combatant waiting area."  To the
west are immense iron double doors which lead into the arena itself. To the
southwest is the seating for Crimson Band members and their dignified guests.
The Hallway of Warriors lies to the east of this corridor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
