This open-air area is situated above and to the northwest of the arena. From
this point, combatants prepare themselves for the challenges to be faced in
the arena below. Farther to the south can be seen a balcony upon which are
chairs in neat rows. A stairway leads to the arena entrance and a ramp leads
down into the arena itself.
